{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Part I: THE LAST SURVIVOR</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/3gif.gif?t=1738900640\" />Sixteen years have passed since humanity's extinction due to a global virus outbreak. You play as James, who, along with his brother, believes they are the last survivors. However, this changes when he discovers an invitation to a survivors' base, <i>HaustVille</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Part II: WHATEVER IT TAKES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/WalkGif.gif?t=1738900640\" />Determined to find others, the brothers leave everything behind. After a few days, they reach <i>HaustVille</i>, but something feels wrong about this village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Part III: THEY ARE GONE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/FoggyVille.gif?t=1738900640\" />&quot;<i>Where is everyone? What happened here?</i>&quot; The player must explore HaustVille to uncover the mystery behind the villagers' disappearance and learn more about the virus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/1gif.gif?t=1738900640\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Developed using <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong>, utilizing cutting-edge technology for a fully immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The entire village is waiting to be explored. And every place has a story to tell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the past through environmental storytelling, speech echoes, and objects left behind by other survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A hostile world awaits, where the virus has not only decimated the population but made animals more aggressive. Caution is essential in the wilderness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience cinematic cutscenes that intensify the narrative.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/5.gif?t=1738900640\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Not today","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/ba0be199c9f18270f4a5f668c11dfb05bd84f718.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to HaustVille","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/14072ca893986055b4580e2231a31adb960b13a0.jpg"},{"name":"Still Got It!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/d8529f4d08f80d6fae64c78f61bbd36b3ad1411d.jpg"},{"name":"57","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/366a0874ec3f675d1cc3cdb59088f1741035b50e.jpg"},{"name":"Join the Hearings","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/0745df73ba1ab236208a6f84a36ee5f86070e7be.jpg"},{"name":"Let There Be Light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/780bf8b1fdd1ba13dc1ab10594774519af92f2eb.jpg"},{"name":"Salvation Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/2ed8f77cc323c14fd5b33f7c77d5f96f52e9b25d.jpg"},{"name":"Meet Us in the Fields at Dawn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/b8d9e063d4bd584c0f62fb130159bf2fc7b919a4.jpg"},{"name":"No Stone Unturned","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2336440/efca15e1b7923fe720d858588e818424cec40e39.jpg"},{